          <int-org-section id="SADC.IO.64" sllink="SLSDOC" slsdocrf="INT-ORG-SECTREF">
               <heading>Council of Ministers</heading>
               <p id="SADC.IO.21">Representatives of SADC member countries at ministerial level meet twice a year to oversee the functioning and development of the organization.</p>
          </int-org-section>
          <int-org-section id="SADC.444" sllink="SLSDOC" slsdocrf="INT-ORG-SECTREF">
               <heading>Organ on Politics, Defence and Security</heading>
               <p>The Organ was established in 1996, although its legal framework was not formalized until the adoption of a Protocol on Politics, Defence and Security Co-operation in August 2001. A troika, comprising the Organ’s current, incoming and outgoing chairpersons, reports directly to the SADC Summit.</p>
